  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to the world of Roboggled where you take control of a clever little robot on a mission to outsmart tricky environments and deliver crates to their precise drop zones. Sound easy? You'll also need to use or avoid the environment in order to solve each puzzle, which includes lasers, conveyor belts, mirrors, teleporters and more! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Contains 60 levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Includes a level editor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Play levels created by others.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Upload your levels to share them with others. (Must create an account and be logged in)</p>",
